-- San Miguel’s Petron Makes Offer for Esso Malaysia
-- B y   C e c i l i a   Y a p
-- 2012-03-19T08:28:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-19/san-miguel-s-petron-makes-offer-for-esso-malaysia-correct-.html
San Miguel Corp. (SMC)  said a  Petron
Corp. (PCOR)  affiliate submitted a mandatory takeover offer to acquire
35 percent of  Esso Malaysia Bhd. (ESSO)   The offer was required following Petron Oil and Gas
International Bhd.’s purchase of 65 percent of Esso Malaysia,
which is expected to be completed on March 30, San Miguel said
in a disclosure to the stock exchange today. The offer price is
3.59 ringgit a share, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cecilia Yap in Manila at 
 cyap19@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
